      <title>G1：警方建议对博索纳罗提起珠宝案指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/police-recommend-charges-against-bolsonaro-in-jewelry-probe-g1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地网站 G1 周四报道，巴西联邦警察在调查涉嫌非法出售沙特阿拉伯和巴林政府赠送的礼物后，建议对前总统雅伊尔·博索纳罗提起刑事指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/police-recommend-charges-against-bolsonaro-in-jewelry-probe-g1</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:05:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
